{"tid":1131960,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"為何香港的音樂頒獎禮總是不能改為評審制？","createTime":"2019-04-30T03:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T17:07:19.000Z","uid":100680,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3efd491481035eef427a3cd46ee930e31a185772","tid":1131960,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:49:22.000Z","msg":"美國的grammy，和台灣的金曲獎<br />\n都是由專業的音樂業界人士，樂評人，音樂學院成員成立選委進行三輪既作品遴選，得出最後結果。<br />\n也因為是由專業人士評選，所以有時會有爆冷的得獎結果（例如2015年grammy的最佳年度專輯個個都以為會係beyonce或者Ed Sheeran或者Sam Smith得獎，結果爆哂冷由beck這個搖滾歌手得獎，）<br />\n<br />\n而香港的音樂頒獎禮，係根據所謂電台播放率，網上投票，現場投票，黎選出所謂的「最受歡迎」總言而之就係根據＂人氣＂而不是＂音樂質素＂"},{"pid":"90091f07aa6a790916c81759d96969c0111756a5","tid":1131960,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:56:55.000Z","msg":"香港啲音樂人本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567b8a9ac5514c6c585d53105b808e2240038ab2","tid":1131960,"uid":100680,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"另外美國grammy和台灣金曲獎<br />\n都無所謂ge「最受歡迎」獎項<br />\n<br />\n台灣金曲獎喺2006年學香港咁搞左個最受歡迎男女歌手獎<br />\n結果俾台灣人圍屌，最後取消左個獎"},{"pid":"c406d9920f70e1bba22ff785ba88b5137ef3324c","tid":1131960,"uid":72195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"香港都有個係評審制，又係一班音樂人選出黎<br />\n但係無人理咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5963c9127dec18dd06da4252e10760f22d022936","tid":1131960,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"台灣的金曲獎都係得啖笑啦<br />\n<br />\n張靚穎 韓紅果d咁勁都拎唔到<br />\n<br />\n香港d歌手有幾多讀音樂出生呀<br />\n<br />\n識西評咩  叫佢地去做評判仲好睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4a99c9fe2416d734d31f8a1f05d8d123d1e6a8","tid":1131960,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"音樂學院，香港好多大學都係教古典<br />\n得IVE 有數碼音樂及媒體高級文憑<br />\n伯樂音樂學院擔當呢個角色又冇乜認受性<br />\n<br />\nbtw 香港冇呢類學校:<br />\nThe Top 10 Colleges for Jazz, Rock, and Popular Music Performance<br />\n<a href=\"https://musicschoolcentral.com/top-10-colleges-for-jazz-rock-and-popular-music-performance/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmusicschoolcentral.com%2Ftop-10-colleges-for-jazz-rock-and-popular-music-performance%2F&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=9e720f0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://musicschoolcentral.com/top-10-colleges-for-jazz-rock-and-popular-music-performance/</a>"},{"pid":"502787c8352713aa7b221e9744369e295b42556f","tid":1131960,"uid":188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:18:56.000Z","msg":"係老屎忽圍爐情況下　你轉一萬次制都無用"},{"pid":"410645939711aa7307c7dd27a4daacd0d7732f0c","tid":1131960,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:36:09.000Z","msg":"台灣流行音樂學系<br />\n<a href=\"https://dimi.tw/studio/archives/5899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdimi.tw%2Fstudio%2Farchives%2F5899&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=fbf7b9fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://dimi.tw/studio/archives/5899</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://dimi.tw/store/wp-content/uploads/26133251_1957637004253106_2014583499_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdimi.tw%2Fstore%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F26133251_1957637004253106_2014583499_n.jpg&h=58cb1074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://dimi.tw/store/wp-content/uploads/26102993_1957637000919773_1967632914_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdimi.tw%2Fstore%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F26102993_1957637000919773_1967632914_n.jpg&h=d30cd799&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db701d4386a4c9b7a745c423c8b4008b22968943","tid":1131960,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"Quote 咗美國台灣流行音樂學系嘅例子<br />\n其實想講，美台兩地都可以將流行音樂推上學術層次，而香港流行音樂仍然停留喺娛樂層次，所以香港頒獎禮都係講求娛樂性，所以有「最受歡迎獎」<br />\n香港頒獎禮計播放率嘅話，係鼓勵緊娛樂性、商業性、多人接受嘅音樂，唔鼓勵創造性、破格嘅音樂"},{"pid":"78a2642e2c6f6b24c5049b4f7ff61ac5e324a8b3","tid":1131960,"uid":118240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db701d4386a4c9b7a745c423c8b4008b22968943","tid":1131960,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"Quote 咗美國台灣流行音樂學系嘅例子<br />\n其實想講，美台兩地都可以將流行音樂推上學術層次，而香港流行音樂仍然停留喺娛樂層次，所以香港頒獎禮都係講求娛樂性，所以有「最受歡迎獎」<br />\n香港頒獎禮計播放率嘅話，係鼓勵緊娛樂性、商業性、多人接受嘅音樂，唔鼓勵創造性、破格嘅音樂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"所以香港音樂冇進步過，甚至係退步緊"},{"pid":"56d59a7c8b2ba6eb098a156eff00d99947dfbf04","tid":1131960,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T06:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13996a377f9d6cb6cc7882232a5b6506abf5176","tid":1131960,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a013a737e5abb591075c8a0cb7a090f8b4e3a1b","tid":1131960,"uid":184592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78a2642e2c6f6b24c5049b4f7ff61ac5e324a8b3","tid":1131960,"uid":118240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db701d4386a4c9b7a745c423c8b4008b22968943","tid":1131960,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"Quote 咗美國台灣流行音樂學系嘅例子<br />\n其實想講，美台兩地都可以將流行音樂推上學術層次，而香港流行音樂仍然停留喺娛樂層次，所以香港頒獎禮都係講求娛樂性，所以有「最受歡迎獎」<br />\n香港頒獎禮計播放率嘅話，係鼓勵緊娛樂性、商業性、多人接受嘅音樂，唔鼓勵創造性、破格嘅音樂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"所以香港音樂冇進步過，甚至係退步緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T16:45:35.000Z","msg":"我相信一直都有人製作好音樂，只不過一般大眾唔會主動去發掘，而造好音樂嘅人又接觸唔到大眾<br />\n而頒獎禮都係頒俾easy listening嘅尋常廣東歌，一般大眾都係睇年度頒獎禮先知有乜新歌，所以有錯覺以為新廣東歌好悶<br />\n<br />\n舉兩個例子，王菀之<br />\n2017年作品《突然一